query: ATTACH MATERIALIZED VIEW default.fact_enforced_5min_mv UUID '85523446-7d55-4846-a908-49451da6a573' TO default.fact_enforced_5min_local (`sg_name` LowCardinality(String), `start_time_5min` DateTime, `int_ipv4` IPv4, `app_key` LowCardinality(String), `line` LowCardinality(String), `pipe` LowCardinality(String), `vc` LowCardinality(String), `tether_indication` LowCardinality(String), `app_group_key` LowCardinality(String), `subscriber_key` String, `volume_in` UInt64, `volume_out` UInt64, `degrade_volume_in` UInt64, `degrade_volume_out` UInt64, `drop_connections` UInt64, `bandwidth_in` Float64, `bandwidth_out` Float64) AS SELECT sg_name, start_time_5min, int_ipv4, app_key, line, pipe, vc, tether_indication, app_group_key, subscriber_key, volume_in, volume_out, degrade_volume_in, degrade_volume_out, drop_connections, bandwidth_in, bandwidth_out FROM default.fact_conv_5min_local WHERE (degrade_volume_in > 0) OR (degrade_volume_out > 0) OR (drop_connections > 0)
